    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Lane Pusher</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077320/extras/db072e88973deeaa0edbbd10d3596335.poster.avif?t=1771842741\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077320/extras/db072e88973deeaa0edbbd10d3596335.webm?t=1771842741\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077320/extras/db072e88973deeaa0edbbd10d3596335.mp4?t=1771842741\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Breeze of Ashes 是一款深受各类推线游戏启发的策略游戏。在大多数模式和地图中，主要目标是摧毁敌方核心。不同模式会改变规则，为你带来多样挑战。在主力舰上堆叠各种模块和自动武器，扭转战局。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077320/extras/d5415bb3f1093623e78af6f7f4f70aeb.poster.avif?t=1771842741\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077320/extras/d5415bb3f1093623e78af6f7f4f70aeb.webm?t=1771842741\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077320/extras/d5415bb3f1093623e78af6f7f4f70aeb.mp4?t=1771842741\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >快速开始</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077320/extras/2dceaf13e53f743f87f9643d07b10cd1.poster.avif?t=1771842741\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077320/extras/2dceaf13e53f743f87f9643d07b10cd1.webm?t=1771842741\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077320/extras/2dceaf13e53f743f87f9643d07b10cd1.mp4?t=1771842741\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >部分地图会提供初始预算，让你部署和建造起始基地及部队。该阶段的生产和建造都是即时完成的。请迅速做出决策，因为时间有限。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >战役</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077320/extras/0ac771507663164425223d85901367d2.poster.avif?t=1771842741\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077320/extras/0ac771507663164425223d85901367d2.webm?t=1771842741\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077320/extras/0ac771507663164425223d85901367d2.mp4?t=1771842741\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >有两条独立战役等待着你。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>大战役</strong>让你面对众多派系。征服提供帝国收益的省份。通过三条发展路径（包括专门的胜利路径）提升你的帝国实力。用你的部队与敌人交战，并通过你派系独有的卡牌决定战斗结果。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077320/extras/bd3a5b7bd016129c4b30ed5143fad40a.poster.avif?t=1771842741\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077320/extras/bd3a5b7bd016129c4b30ed5143fad40a.webm?t=1771842741\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077320/extras/bd3a5b7bd016129c4b30ed5143fad40a.mp4?t=1771842741\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在<strong>护航战役</strong>中，你需要在殖民地发展与舰队建设之间找到平衡。战役长度和难度设定决定了你需要救援的人数以取得胜利。救生艇来源于你的军队，因此会削弱你在任务中的战力。在过程中，你将解锁技术，即使本次任务失败，也可以带入下一轮尝试。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >殖民地</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过建造具有特殊功能和收益的建筑发展殖民地。每个建筑都有使用次数限制，限制扩张。拆除建筑会略微改善其下方地块，并返还一次使用次数。你需要完成一系列目标，但这里是你的安全空间，可以专注于建造最有效率的殖民地。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Boss 战</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077320/extras/414d11bbf5930ccde589a9b93b95f87a.poster.avif?t=1771842741\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077320/extras/414d11bbf5930ccde589a9b93b95f87a.webm?t=1771842741\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077320/extras/414d11bbf5930ccde589a9b93b95f87a.mp4?t=1771842741\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >有一个专门的游戏模式让你挑战 Boss。整个地图都会试图击败你，因此直接冲向 Boss 或摧毁其生产设施可能是明智的选择。你还可以设计自己的 Boss 并与之对战，或者挑战预设或社区创建的 Boss。赢得“Boss 对 Boss”战斗可以提升你的分数。目前，你的最后一个 Boss 会上传排行榜，并作为遭遇供其他玩家挑战。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>主要特色:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 推线策略玩法，模块化主力舰搭配自动攻击武器</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 多种游戏模式和地图，规则与目标不断变化</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 两条独立战役线，配备持久进度系统</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 战役中的安全殖民地或独立小规模战斗的建设玩法</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 自定义 Boss 创造</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 以<strong>单人模式</strong>为主，同时支持多人模式</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >这款游戏适合你吗？</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Breeze of Ashes 面向喜欢战略规划、系统互动叠加，并能在压力下做出关键决策的玩家。如果你喜欢推线玩法、不对称派系以及奖励长期思考的战役，你会觉得这里很适合自己。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >如果你希望体验纯动作游戏、传统 RTS（包含密集微操）或纯叙事体验，那么这款游戏可能不适合你。</p>",
